{"tid":2273507,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"匡智醜聞︱匡智會去年總收入逾10億元 前警務處助理處長林文榮任總幹事兼松嶺村總監","createTime":"2020-11-05T19:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T14:05:02.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ba3399ae6545e643b02bcfe45ad4b274e103496f","tid":2273507,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T19:53:24.000Z","msg":"匡智松嶺村的管理問多多，題前爆虐兒醜聞，又涉及逼有行為問題的學生退宿等投訴。現任匡智會總幹事兼松嶺村辦事處總監林文榮並非社福界出身，而是前警務處助理處長。他於2017年1月離開警隊，並於同年12月出任匡智會總幹事。工黨立法會議員張超雄指出，殘疾復康機構掌舵人多為社福界出身或具社工背景，由警察背景人士出任總幹事並不多見，強調社福是一門專業，「用一個非呢方面出身嘅人管理，我唔會話一定唔得，但呢個會挑戰大」。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，2015年9月，兩名匡智東頭宿舍職員被指向拒絕進食的智障院友灌湯，用索帶固定院友並壓迫其臉龐令其張口，導致院友面部瘀傷，被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。惟最終律政司在裁判官建議下，撤銷控罪並准二人各自簽2,000元守行為兩年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/J7K57TL45RHWLDTUKOY2U2R6ME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FJ7K57TL45RHWLDTUKOY2U2R6ME%2F&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8kXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=266a3cf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FJ7K57TL45RHWLDTUKOY2U2R6ME%2F&h=16d0584e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/J7K57TL45RHWLDTUKOY2U2R6ME/</a>"},{"pid":"9cfb7ca79508fb0b6ab5e75476592f9a3d9eae09","tid":2273507,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T19:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b545927bd96da2492ba5912538c130f8a1b40cf6","tid":2273507,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T20:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl